The FBI has clearly ignored Hunter Biden and his laptop and corruption, Hillary with her offsite server who with the aid of the FBI destroyed evidence, and Eric Holder whose Fast and Furious program killed reportedly (by one newspaper) at least 300 Mexicans. And yet Democrats are willing to even make up charges to throw their political opponents in jail.
